# Dvorak compatibility
map h scroll left
map t scroll down
map n scroll up
map s scroll right
map l search forward
map L search backward

# Options
set sandbox none
set statusbar-h-padding 0
set statusbar-v-padding 0
set page-padding        1
set selection-clipboard clipboard

# Shortcuts
map i zoom in
map d zoom out
map u scroll half-up
map o srcoll half-down
map c recolor
map r reload
map e quit
map P print
map R rotate
